00:15:13.580 --> 00:15:15.390
Magkaiba kayo ni Mi So noong ipinanganak ka.

00:15:15.890 --> 00:15:17.220
Kaya sana huwag mong gawin ito.

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:19.090
Se Ri, pakiusap.

00:15:19.820 --> 00:15:22.160
