hindi ibig sabihin na may kailangang magbago.

00:18:29.110 --> 00:18:31.550
Naiintindihan mo ba ang sinasabi ko?

00:18:35.490 --> 00:18:36.490
Kyung Chae...

00:18:38.220 --> 00:18:39.220
Hindi.

00:18:40.390 --> 00:18:43.460
Ibig mong sabihin, wala ka namang pinagkaiba
sa nanay na nagpalaki sa akin.

00:18:45.660 --> 00:18:46.730
Tama iyan.

00:18:49.470 --> 00:18:51.400
Sa isang sulyap ng kapalaran,

00:18:53.070 --> 00:18:55.410
